author_ssm: Annie Grunow.  Accretion processed by John Bence.
abstract_ssm: This collection consists of the papers of Eliot Freidson, a professor of sociology at New York University from 1961 to 1993. The material consists of files relating to the books he wrote and the courses he taught.
